GULF OF MEXICO.
FLORIDA TO MEXICO.
1. M/V JET BARGES 200 WITH THREE GREY BARGES,
   TOTAL LENGTH 150 FEET, UNREPORTED
   CAPTIVA ISLAND (26-32N 82-12W) TO

   IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP
   LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO
